点评网站 Yelp 上给他们最低评价。 11 月 22 日，大量特斯拉粉丝涌入摩根大通的 Yelp 页面，打出大量一星差评，目前页面已暂停评论。 来源：老板联播、 21 世纪经济报道"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-e642e604e9fce9003f18daa8266f164d_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "111 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/501300015"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4Iltiw9uSqt8haEAMaCDczNjgxMjAzINby94wGMAc4bUAccgk1MDEzMDAwMTV4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "29_1637924514.8241122", "card_id": "Q_501607055", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 51}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价 OPPO Reno7 系列的定价策略？在当下市场能否复制 Reno5 系列的业绩？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "Reno5 系列让 OPPO 重回份额 TOP2，Reno6 延续了 OPPO 份额，面对升配置维持价格的 Reno7，以及相关竞品态势，如何看待这一定价策略对 OPPO 产品价位段的维持和促进？能否有销量预期？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-5ca1b8faa6d4eeed246baeb876d710ef_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "85 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/501607055"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4Iltiw9uSqt8haEAMaCDczNzQ5NDc3IKmW/owGMAE4UkAdcgk1MDE2MDcwNTV4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "30_1637924514.8246217", "card_id": "Q_269994322", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 51}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "刚刚毕业的大学生进投行可拿到多高的工资？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picb.zhimg.com/50/v2-b151acc1bfab53e70699fdc183025681_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "73 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/269994322"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Iltiw9uSqt8haEAMaCDIyMjc0MDMyIK6p49UFMAE44gNAHnIJMjY5OTk0MzIyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "31_1637924514.8249216", "card_id": "Q_501164962", "feed_s